sequenceDiagram
    actor P1 as Player 1
    actor P2 as Player 2
    actor P3 as Player 3
    participant GE as game_engine
    participant SR as ScoringRule::PositionRace

    Note over P1,SR: correct_answer_count resets to 0 at question start

    GE->>P1: question N
    GE->>P2: question N
    GE->>P3: question N

    P1->>GE: submit_answer (correct, arrives 1st)
    GE->>GE: correct_answer_count = 1
    GE->>SR: position_points(1) → 1000
    GE-->>P1: answer_result {points: 1000, position: 1}

    P2->>GE: submit_answer (correct, arrives 2nd)
    GE->>GE: correct_answer_count = 2
    GE->>SR: position_points(2) → 750
    GE-->>P2: answer_result {points: 750, position: 2}

    P3->>GE: submit_answer (incorrect)
    Note over GE: count NOT incremented for wrong answers
    GE-->>P3: answer_result {points: 0, position: null}
